{
  "stem": "21762.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was back and forth, the Germans, and then Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I met the Germans on the road.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They give me cookies.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They asked me if I got some guns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I says, I got a knife.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't bother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They give me-- they give cookies for the kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they went further.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when they go, they had a white flag that means they don't bother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we was together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the war started, I wasn't already in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was already on the road.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was thinking I go through a town [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had relatives there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was thinking, I'm going to stay in [NON-ENGLISH] with the relatives until the war wouldn't be too long, because Poland is not so big.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this wasn't like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the people lately, everybody went for himself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had my brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother was riding a bike after me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My brother's wife with a child, my wife with two kids, my wife's sisters, two girls, and some neighbors.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly where.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't took anything, because I was thinking I'll just go for a day or two.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even I didn't pick my father's picture from the wall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was sorry leaving, but too late.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't took nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just took our to cover up, pillow and a big-- how you call a big [INAUDIBLE] bed?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Big blanket.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what I took to cover up the kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Money was not much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I sold the gasoline.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had money.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't have not much money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then you were saying by the time you got to with the horse and buggy, where were you?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With the horse and wagon, I was to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
